Please check below point for optimization.&lt;br/&gt;
1. Use `UNION ALL` instead of `OR` for little bit faster.&lt;br/&gt;
2. Break your code in `small small part`&lt;br/&gt;
3. Use table `alias` instead of `full qualified name` in column selection. So it will take `less characters` in `dynamic query`.&lt;br/&gt;
4. Please use column name instead of * in CTE column selection also.&lt;br/&gt;
5. Please use `sp_executesql` SP for dynamic query. Check this [link][1] for more knowledge.&lt;br/&gt;

